<import src="/template/myTemplate.wxml"></import>
<view class="container">
  <!-- 导航 -->
  <scroll-view enable-flex scroll-with-animation class="navScroll">
    <view id="{{'scroll'+ item.id}}" class="navItem">
      <view class="navContent {{navId == 0?'active':'' }}" bindtap="changNav" data-id="0">
        品牌介绍
      </view>
    </view>
    <view id="{{'scroll'+ item.id}}" class="navItem">
      <view class="navContent {{navId == 1?'active':'' }}" bindtap="changNav" data-id="1">
        专利认证
      </view>
    </view>
    <view id="{{'scroll'+ item.id}}" class="navItem">
      <view class="navContent {{navId == 2?'active':'' }}" bindtap="changNav" data-id="2">
        售后保险
      </view>
    </view>
    <view id="{{'scroll'+ item.id}}" class="navItem">
      <view class="navContent {{navId == 3?'active':'' }}" bindtap="changNav" data-id="3">
        加入我们
      </view>
    </view>
  </scroll-view>

  <!-- 内容列表 -->
  <view class="centenItem {{navId == 0?'centenActive':'' }}">
    <view class="wrap" style="padding-bottom: 60rpx;">
      <template is="detail" data="{{...item}}"></template>

      <view class="imgItem">
        <image mode="widthFix"
          src="https://img13.360buyimg.com/ddimg/jfs/t1/139402/10/16741/18043/5fc84ebcE5f1d0e5b/a3e0f7f79ea65e5e.jpg" />
      </view>

      <text class="contenItem">
             
         漆面装甲，高端汽车漆面保护膜专业品牌运营商，依托于云林膜业十数年的技术沉淀，创新并应用最适合中国环境的TPH/TPU基材和高分子氟碳晶化涂层技术工艺制作，产品稳定、抗冲击性能一流，可以最大限度的保护原厂车漆免受外力损伤。 
         
             
         漆面装甲高端汽车漆面保护膜作为汽车美容市场的新贵，完全按照国家工信部《车身贴》、《汽车漆面保护膜》行业标准生产，通过了SGS国际商检和ITS双重检验。其强大的产品性能，也使之成为汽车后市场广大经销商认可的专项盈利项目。
      </text>
    </view>



  </view>
  <view class="centenItem {{navId == 1?'centenActive':'' }}">
    <view class="wrap" style="padding-bottom: 60rpx;">
      <template is="detail" data="{{...item}}"></template>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="centenItem {{navId == 2?'centenActive':'' }}">
    <view class="wrap" style="padding-bottom: 60rpx;">
      <template is="detail" data="{{...item}}"></template>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="centenItem {{navId == 3?'centenActive':'' }}">
    <view class="wrap" style="padding-bottom: 60rpx;">
      <template is="detail" data="{{...item}}"></template>

      <view class="wrapper">
        <view class="titleItem">请输入以下信息，之后会有我们的工作人员联系您。</view>
        <!-- 门店名称 -->
        <view class="box-wrapper">
          <view class="tag-wrapper">门店名称：</view>
          <view class="input-wrapper">
            <input type="text" value="" placeholder="请输入门店名称" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
          </view>
        </view>
        <!-- 门店地址 -->
        <view class="box-wrapper">
          <view class="tag-wrapper">门店地址：</view>
          <view class="input-wrapper">
            <input type="text" value="" placeholder="请输入门店地址" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
          </view>
        </view>
        <!-- 联系人姓名： -->
        <view class="box-wrapper">
          <view class="tag-wrapper">联系人姓名：</view>
          <view class="input-wrapper">
            <input type="text" value="" placeholder="请输入联系人姓名" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
          </view>
        </view>
        <!-- 联系电话： -->
        <view class="box-wrapper">
          <view class="tag-wrapper">联系电话：</view>
          <view class="input-wrapper">
            <input type="number" value="" placeholder="请输入联系电话" placeholder-class="placeholder" />
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="submit-wrapper">
          <button hover-class="but-hover" bindtap="toDetails">提交</button>
        </view>

        <view class="textItem">或</view>

        <view class="codeItem">
          <view class="codeImg">
            <image src=""></image>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="textItem" style="padding-bottom: 14rpx;">全国招商热线：186 6587 7758</view>
        <view class="textItem">客户服务：400-9988-078</view>





      </view>



    </view>



  </view>

  <template is="footer" data="{{...item}}"></template>




</view>